* Segal, Hugh (April 23, 2016). &quot;Two Freedoms: Canada&#x27;s Global Future&quot;. Dundurn Press. .
* Segal, Hugh (January 31, 2011). &quot;The Right Balance: Canada&#x27;s Conservative Tradition&quot;. Douglas &amp; McIntyre. .
* Segal, Hugh (November 7, 2006). &quot;The Long Road Back: The Conservative Journey, 1993-2006&quot;. HarperCollins Publishers. .
* Segal, Hugh (March 18, 2005). &quot;Geopolitical Integrity&quot;. Institute for Research on Public Policy. 
* Segal, Hugh (2000). &quot;In defence of civility: Reflections of a recovering politician&quot;. Stoddart Publishing. 
* Segal, Hugh (1997). &quot;Beyond greed: a traditional conservative confronts neoconservative excess&quot;. Stoddart Publishing. .
* Segal, Hugh (1996). &quot;No Surrender: Reflections of a Tory Warrior&quot;. HarperCollins Canada. .
